{"tid":1576625,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逆權運動】張祝珊中學建議聯群結隊離校  防白衣人襲擊","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T16:07:58.000Z","uid":227801,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d221d26472977769a8e70973ba254b165fa5b46e","tid":1576625,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190917/60054576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F60054576&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F1FFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=38b8db19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F60054576&h=33922f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190917/60054576</a><br />\n炮台山及北角日前再次發生白衣人施襲事件，區內中學張祝珊英文中學學生昨日（16日）聯同鄰校發起「一齊返學」行動，免落單而遭白衣人襲擊，更有傳言指曾有同學離校時遭白衣人襲擊。校方回覆《蘋果》查詢時稱，無收到同學遇襲的報告或求助；該校另就近日襲擊事件採取相關措施，包括建議學生聯群一起離校，甚至安排老師或教練陪同學生到港鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n校方稱今日向家長發通告，說明學校保障學生安全的相關措施，強烈建議同學放學後立即回家，勿在街上流連；該校同學一貫須於6時前離開學校，校方建議同學「聯群結隊，以相照應」；若因參與課外活動於6時後才離開，校方已要求老師或教練在可能情況下陪伴同學到港鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n校方續稱，學校亦會加強監察附近環境，遇有可疑人物會報警，並要求學生留校至情況安全才離開，同學若於街上遇險，可即時回校暫避；又建議同學乘搭直達校門的公共交通工具，減少於北角及炮台山港鐵站一帶逗留，若須乘搭港鐵可考慮到天后站。如有需要，校方會隨時暫停有關課外活動；若家長不放心，可接送同學回校，亦可為同學請假缺席課堂或課外活動。"},{"pid":"736d29af423e46957ba9b423f1a22ec6a75f77ab","tid":1576625,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"850adaf7a1ead35cfdcdca593c15b311f4d457eb","tid":1576625,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"支持達狗母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0212319258afbdf1cef366e1c050047b85edfebb","tid":1576625,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2972a78aa812e482ee07c6c3a819e79cb787f7","tid":1576625,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a75c76afd4e53345450a4f1badf132b0a1c68b","tid":1576625,"uid":255840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"850adaf7a1ead35cfdcdca593c15b311f4d457eb","tid":1576625,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"支持達狗母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"絲打唔好提佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以佢為恥"},{"pid":"bcf4dc8e22d4d5bf98ce4d265de9e4a009fbdce8","tid":1576625,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c5bffae372686d351253eaeae955ddefa8b6a1","tid":1576625,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nDsaRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nDsaRN.jpg&h=7c2f6d45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCiotDt